| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0082 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 40cf93de-ce0e-560c-b44a-4f5c1876f7d1"
